TITLE: Episode 42 - The Big Tech Mask Falls Off
DESCRIPTION: This week, Facebook and Twitter both made a New York Post article completely disappear from their platforms. In this special episode, Thaddeus and Gary talk about the consequences of this shocking level of censorship.
